BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune in 7th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Aries 10°48’) in natal 7th House \n \nThis transit brings complications to partner relationships. The person you love may seem more distant, or you may be too demanding and expect too much. Their behaviour may be frustrating for you. Try to accept your partner for who he or she is and realize that you cannot control the other person; you should just love him or her unconditionally. If you’re single, you may be attracted to people who will hurt you. It is unlikely that you will meet the right person during this transit, so be careful if you meet a new romantic partner.  In business relationship be aware of misunderstandings, vagueness (in negotiations or contracts) or even deceit. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20290609T023900Z
DTEND:20290609T023900Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165825Z
UID:4_tr_ne_in_h
END:VEVENT
