BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Pluto in 5th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Pluto (Aquarius 15°45’) in natal 5th House \n \nTransit Pluto in this house will bring aggressiveness or at least less tolerance into your love life. You might want to change your partner’s behaviour that bothers you and you may even use force. You will be more realistic. You should also expect more drama and a greater desire for relationships that will be much more intense and passionate. You may also have the tendency to play games and cause conflicts just to spice up your relationship. If you are single, it is possible that you will enter a relationship that will cause an intense transformation and change your life. If you have children, expect problems caused by their rebellious behaviour. Beware of your tendency towards manipulative behaviour and the tendency to control things around you.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20330308T130900Z
DTEND:20330308T130900Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165825Z
UID:9_tr_pl_in_h
END:VEVENT
