BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune in 8th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Taurus 7°46’) in natal 8th House \n \nDuring this period, you may encounter problems in shared finances or assets. You may also unexpectedly come across a loan or other form of financial support. If your partner or relative is facing financial problems, it will also affect your life. You will experience a revival in intimate relationships, but they may be slightly confusing. You long for mental connection with your partner, and if you don’t have it, you may choose to end the relationship or not enter otherwise promising new relationship.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
