BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus in 11th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Leo 15°45’) in natal 11th House \n \nTransit Uranus in the 11th house will bring unconventional and original people to your life. The circle of people you meet may change and it will be easy for you to make new friends. You will be attracted to bohemian people. You will be able to see people for who they really are, and you will not be judgemental. The question is whether your friendship with these people will last for a long time or it will end as soon as the transit is over. This house also affects your dreams and aspirations that will now be more idealistic than usual.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20420920T231300Z
DTEND:20420920T231300Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165825Z
UID:18_tr_ur_in_h
END:VEVENT
