SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus in 12th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Virgo 15°35’) in natal 12th House \n \nThis transit helps you to break free of the cycles and burdens you are not aware of and that cause obstacles on your way. Various events or coincidences may occur at the beginning of this process. There is a risk that your secrets or private information will be revealed. You will have the desire to help others selflessly and anonymously.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
