BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Pluto in 6th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Pluto (Pisces 15°35’) in natal 6th House \n \nYou should be careful not to sacrifice yourself during this transit. Pluto in this house brings a desire to selflessly help others, but you must not overdo it. It teaches you to overcome pain, disappointment and hypersensitivity. It also teaches you not to be full of yourself and deal with your failures. These processes are necessary to create a new integrated personality. It is a good time to undergo therapy. You should keep to your daily routine and exercise regularly. It is also important that you maintain a healthy diet and try to detoxify and regenerate your body. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20550923T050500Z
DTEND:20550923T050500Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165825Z
UID:33_tr_pl_in_h
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune in 9th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Gemini 8°44’) in natal 9th House \n \nYou will have the desire to expand your spirituality. You may be interested in spiritual teachings and metaphysics. You may experience a burst of creativity, which will be especially beneficial for you if you make a living by writing. If you are still studying, you will have difficulty concentrating for long periods of time and you will find it hard to study. You will long to be near water sources. Confusion and misunderstandings associated with travel, legal matters, or university education may occur.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
