BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus in 2nd House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Scorpio 7°46’) in natal 2nd House \n \nThis transit will make you think about your values. Approaches and beliefs that do not serve your greater good need to be removed and replaced by those that benefit you. For some people, this transit marks a shift to less materialistic way of life. There will be changes in the area of finance. Your source of income may change, and areas connected to Uranus, for example technology, science, computers or metaphysics may become your main source of income. You may also choose to work as a freelancer. You may be more willing to take risks that will help you earn better income. However, be cautious because Uranus may bring fluctuations in your income so you can make a lot of money but also quickly lose it.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
