BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus in 3rd House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Sagittarius 8°44’) in natal 3rd House \n \nThanks to this transit, you will experience a period of great mental stimulation and change. You will want to learn new things or start studying a new field. This enthusiasm may not last long, but you will still be looking for a way to express yourself and you will do great especially in writing and public speaking. You will be interested in unusual ideas, disciplines and thoughts. This will open new horizons and help you break free from your daily routine. You may also want to change your look and improve your image.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
