BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune in 10th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Cancer 12°27’) in natal 10th House \n \nNeptune in this house gives you the clarity of where you are going in life. However, it also causes inner uneasiness and confusion. If you are someone who always has a plan and your wellbeing depends on being able to adhere to the plan, you will adapt less well to this transit than someone who is more flexible. Other people may have distorted opinions about you, and they may not be able to see who you really are. Try to show them your true self. You may experience problems with older people.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
