BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus in 4th House
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Capricorn 12°27’) in natal 4th House \n \nDuring this transit you may experience problems at home in the form of unexpected changes to your plans, the need for repairs or changes in routines. Moving is likely, especially if you have natal or transit Mars in this house. Unexpected changes to your plans will test your patience. You will also rethink relationships with your family and think about what family means to you.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
